subtests.name: Same-origin prerequisite check: the original prototype is accessible
Same-origin: setting the prototype to an empty object via Object.setPrototypeOf should throw a TypeError
Same-origin: setting the prototype to an empty object via __proto__ should throw a TypeError
Same-origin: setting the prototype to an empty object via Reflect.setPrototypeOf should return false
Same-origin: the prototype must still be null
Same-origin: setting the prototype to null via Object.setPrototypeOf should not throw
Same-origin: setting the prototype to null via __proto__ should not throw
Same-origin: setting the prototype to null via Reflect.setPrototypeOf should return true
